“Set Fire to the Rain” is in Adele’s latest album “21”. Written by Adele and Fraser T. Smith and produced by Smith. The song is still in top singles chart in Belgium, Poland, Holland, Czech Republic, Slovakia, the United States and other countries. In the United States billboard singles chart for 2 weeks singles, but also for the Adele created a new record : Adele is the only artist, who has the 3 songs from the same album in the top Billboard singles chart, the album topped the album charts in Billboard at the same time.
